title: Guest Host (ft. Mina Kimes, David Jacoby, Dianna Russini and Mike Golic Jr.)
description: With Katie under the weather, Ashley and Jay turn to some friends to help get you the Sports? you need this week. They talk FaceSwap and Baseball with Mina Kimes (12:40), The Bubble with David Jacoby (28:33), NFL predictions with Dianna Russini (44:48), and NWSL, The Bachelor, and Reality Shows with Mike Golic Jr. (50:40).
